# sync targets — ABSOLUTE project-root paths, one per line.
# '#' = comment, blank lines ignored. An empty list is a safe no-op.
#
# The sync skill installs this repo's workflow scaffolding (see ../manifest.txt)
# into each root listed below, using one of: --mixed (default) / --soft / --force.
#
# SETUP: copy this file to `list.txt` (which is gitignored) and add your own targets.
#
# Examples (edit for your machine):
# D:\Projects\YourProject
# C:\dev\another-project
# /home/you/projects/your-app
